title: 01-0041_control
growth_protocol_ch1: Muscle biopsy samples extracted from 27 FSHD subjects, and on 8 control quadriceps muscle biopsies from unaffected individuals.
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was extracted from whole cells using NucleoSpin RNA kit (Macherey-Nagel) following the manufacturer's instructions.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: RNA-seq libraries were prepared from total RNA using the TruSeq RNA Sample Prep v2 Kit (Illumina, Inc., San Diego, CA, USA) and a Sciclone  NGSx Workstation (PerkinElmer, Waltham, MA, USA).  RNA-seq libraries were pooled (14-plex) and clustered onto two flow cell lanes.
description: lower extremity muscle biopsy accessible by needle
data_processing: Filtered unqualified raw reads whose filter flag is tagged with ""Y"".
data_processing.1: Trimmed Illumina universal adapters by Trimmomatic-0.32.
data_processing.2: Mapped processed reads to genome built hg38 by Taphat-2.1.0/Bowtie2-2.2.6.
data_processing.3: Counedt reads to the features collected from GENCODE v24 and the Bioconductor funciton GenomicAlignments::summarizedOverlap() and ""iInersectionStrick"" mode were used.
data_processing.4: All the scripts and codes for analysis were depostied in our github repos (https://github.com/Fredhutch/Rwellstone_FSHD_muscle_biopsy) and explained in our gitbook (https://fredhutch.github.io/Rwellstone_FSHD_muscle_biopsy).
data_processing.6: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: year2.dds.rda stored a DESeq2's DESeqDataSet instance including controls and one-year follow-up RNA-seq gene counts matrix along with all MRI/histopathology signals as column data.    year2_column_data.csv stored MRI signals, histopathology signals, phenotype data and marker scores.
data_processing.7: year2_column_data.csv.gz: sample phenotype metedata, follow-up visit sample only
data_processing.8: year2_genecounts.csv.gz: gene counts for the follow-up visit
data_processing.9: year2_normalized_genecounts.csv.gz: normalized gene counts for the follow-up visit
data_processing.10: year2_TPM.csv.gz: TPM gene matrix for initial the follow-up visit
data_processing.11: year2.dds.rda: DESeqDataSet instance storing gene features, gene counts and phenotype metadata, follow-up visit only
